metadata.name: Pi Square
metadata.description:
All 10,000 pixels make sense and proof of my work. Each pixel is filled with the color selected using the Pi number. In the lower left corner, a pixel has a HEX Color Code: 314159 - the first 6 digits of Pi number. 
The next pixel has a code: 265358 - the second 6 digits of Pi, and so on spirals into the middle.
